title: Dana Kellin Diamond Rectangles Necklace
description:
Simple yet sophisticated, Dana Kellin's Diamond Rectangles Necklace showcases the designer's signature gold wire-wrapping technique, surrounding five distinct diamond pave rectangles of increasing size. Dana Kellin jewelry is best known for its intricate, meticulous wire-wrapping details. The labor intensive, time consuming nature of the process results in a balance of organic, handmade charm with an air of refinement and sophistication.

  • Dimensions: Necklace 16.25 in, Bars .4 to .6 in w
  • Materials: 14K gold frames, wire, and chain, diamond pave
